text: Seremban 3 Seremban 3 (Malay: Seremban Tiga) is a satellite town located about six kilometers south west of downtown Seremban in Negeri Sembilan, Malaysia. Seremban 3 also have education centers such as Universiti Teknologi MARA campus in Seremban. However, Seremban 3 also have a shopping place like Unicity Mall and it currently still under construction. Seremban 3 is close to the nearest Rasah Jaya and Mambau. ==Educations== * Universiti Teknologi Mara * SMK Seremban 3 Category:Towns in Negeri Sembilan
